                             CORDS Short Form TX

   Use this form in certain simple cases to request that the copyright for
   a work be registered with the Copyright Office. Click here for Basic
   Information about this form. For help with individual fields, click on
   their titles or similarly highlighted text.

   If you find while completing this form that you should be using the
   "long form," click here:

                             Change to Long Form
     __________________________________________________________________

